    <item>
      <title>英国通货膨胀在里夫斯和削减速度的福音中意外冷却</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-in-boost-for-rate-cut-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通货膨胀意外冷却，加强了英格兰银行在五月再次降低利率的案件，并在周三的重要经济声明之前为富裕人雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的总理提供了士气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-inflation-unexpectedly-slows-in-boost-for-rate-cut-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 07:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国反对派领导人无罪违反选举法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/south-korea-court-sides-with-opposition-leader-in-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国法院裁定，反对派领导人李·詹·蒙（Lee Jae-Myung）没有违反选举法，推翻了下级法院的裁决，并增加了他在未来任何总统选举中竞选的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/south-korea-court-sides-with-opposition-leader-in-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
